            <div class="fs-18 fw-bold f-nunito text-red">
              Integrity and Confidentiality
            </div>
            <p>
              Organizations must implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure the security and
              integrity of personal data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
