            <div class="fs-18 fw-bold f-nunito text-red">
              Data Subject Rights
            </div>
            <p>
              Individuals have the following rights under the DPA: Right to access personal data, Right to
              rectification,
              Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten"), Right to restrict processing, Right to data portability,
              Right to object to processing, Right to be informed about automated decision-making
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
