            <div class="fs-18 fw-bold f-nunito text-red">
              Accountability
            </div>
            <p>
              Organizations are accountable for ensuring compliance with the DPA. They must appoint a data protection
              officer (DPO) and implement appropriate technical and organizational measures.
            </p>
          </div>
